Nava

Mobility + Fintech Super App for Emerging Markets

Nava is an AI-native mobility and financial services platform designed for emerging markets, starting with Africa.

The platform combines ride-hailing, digital payments, wallets, credit scoring, micro-lending, and financial infrastructure into a single scalable ecosystem.

---

Vision

To become the operating system for mobility and financial inclusion across emerging economies.

